{"arkId":"cl010056186","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010056186","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Minerve au milieu de soldats","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Minerve au milieu de soldats"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : XVIIe si\u00e8cle (vers 1670 - 1700)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1670,"endYear":1700,"imprecision":"vers","text":"XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"},{"label":"France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"\u00c9cole de","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Poussin, Nicolas","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"\u00c9cole de","dates":[{"date":"1665","place":"Rome","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1594","place":"Les Andelys","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q41554"},{"label":"Perrier, Fran\u00e7ois","attributionLevel":"Ancienne Attribution","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1650","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1590","place":"Franche-Comt\u00e9 ou Bourgogne","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q82566"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"INV 7324","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"MN 55","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Peintures","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1","displayDimension":"1 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"1,42","displayDimension":"1,42 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"huile sur toile","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Historique\r\nDon Jean Cottini (1802-1876), 1850 (Inscrit dans l\u0027inventaire MN n\u00b0 55) ; d\u00e9pos\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019ambassade de France \u00e0 Istanbul (puis \u00e0 Ankara), 1899 ; retour au Louvre, 2013.\r\n\r\nCommentaire\r\nCe tableau est revenu au Louvre en 2013 apr\u00e8s un d\u00e9p\u00f4t de longue dur\u00e9e \u00e0 l\u2019ambassade de France en Turquie. Il est difficilement visible sous les vernis alt\u00e9r\u00e9s. Le sujet n\u2019est pas identifiable : on peut sans doute reconna\u00eetre Minerve au milieu de soldats. La sc\u00e8ne para\u00eet se d\u00e9rouler en \u00c9gypte si l\u2019on en juge par les pyramides visibles dans le paysage \u00e0 l\u2019arri\u00e8re-plan. Le style est classicisant, empruntant \u00e0 Nicolas Poussin et \u00e0 Charles Le Brun avec une datation probable dans le dernier\r\ntiers du xviie si\u00e8cle. On peut faire le rapprochement avec le cycle d\u00e9di\u00e9 \u00e0 Io peint par Ren\u00e9 Antoine Houasse pour le Grand Trianon \u00e0 partir de 1688.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Cottini, Jean","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Peintures","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Milovanovic, Nicolas, Peintures fran\u00e7aises du XVIIe du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Louvre \u00e9ditions \/ Gallimard, 2021","bibliograp